 does it promise for him?</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-12 eNVkkS dFhhBp">Tim Pears</p></div><div class="sc-d56bc236-6 jrySry"></div></div></a><a href="/essays/on-the-intangible-border-of-the-kogis-sacred-mountains"><div class="sc-d56bc236-9 eCvrmh"><div type="essay" class="sc-82db9615-2 kSWDpk"><img alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 960px) 45vw, (max-width: 1440px) 30vw, 430px" srcSet="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/5d2f0820-5443-450e-9f5b-6416cf320023/essay-h_00149225.jpg?width=256&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 256w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/5d2f0820-5443-450e-9f5b-6416cf320023/essay-h_00149225.jpg?width=384&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 384w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/5d2f0820-5443-450e-9f5b-6416cf320023/essay-h_00149225.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 640w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/5d2f0820-5443-450e-9f5b-6416cf320023/essay-h_00149225.jpg?width=750&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 750w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/5d2f0820-5443-450e-9f5b-6416cf320023/essay-h_00149225.jpg?width=828&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 828w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/5d2f0820-5443-450e-9f5b-6416cf320023/essay-h_00149225.jpg?width=1080&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1080w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/5d2f0820-5443-450e-9f5b-6416cf320023/essay-h_00149225.jpg?width=1200&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1200w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/5d2f0820-5443-450e-9f5b-6416cf320023/essay-h_00149225.jpg?width=1920&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1920w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/5d2f0820-5443-450e-9f5b-6416cf320023/essay-h_00149225.jpg?width=2048&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 2048w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/5d2f0820-5443-450e-9f5b-6416cf320023/essay-h_00149225.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 3840w" src="https://images.aeonmed